        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, tear the <strong>meat-free chicken </strong>into smaller strips</p><p>Once the spring greens have softened, add the<strong> meat-free chicken</strong> to the pan</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
